'''沙查·諾姆·巴隆·科恩'''（{{lang-en|Sacha Noam Baron Cohen}}，{{bd|1971年|10月13日|catIdx=C}}）是一名[[英国|英国]][[男演員|男演員]]、[[喜剧演员|喜剧演员]]、[[編劇|編劇]]和[[監製|監製]]。因在他的[[英國第四台|英國第四台]]電視劇《{{link-en|Ali G個人秀|Da Ali G Show}}》上出演一系列成功而充满争议的角色而出名，其中的Ali G、[[波拉特|波拉特]]及[[波兒出城之妖壇教祖3點「畢露」搞硬美國佬|布魯諾]]更被搬上了大銀幕。拜伦·科恩更因在《[[波拉特_(电影)|波拉特：为建设伟大祖国哈萨克斯坦而学习美国文化]]》中演活波拉特一角而獲得多項獎項，包括[[金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇類電影男主角|金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇類電影男主角]]，並提名了[[奧斯卡最佳改編劇本獎|奧斯卡最佳改編劇本獎]]。

這些富争议性的角色最初只出現於《Da Ali G Show》中，但自2002年的《{{link-en|誰與爭瘋|Ali G Indahouse}}》開始，到《[[波叔出城|波叔出城]]》及《[[波兒出城之妖壇教祖3點「畢露」搞硬美國佬|布魯諾出城]]》，高漢很有可能會把電視劇中的所有角色都改編成電影。2011年後，他又出演了《[[雨果的冒險|雨果的冒險]]》（2011年）、《[[大鈍裁者|大鈍裁者]]》（2012年）及《[[悲慘世界_(2012年電影)|悲慘世界]]》（2012年）。

==早年生平==
拜伦·柯恩出生于英国伦敦[[漢默史密斯|漢默史密斯]]，毕业于[[剑桥大学基督学院|剑桥大学基督学院]]历史系。他的母親Daniella Naomi（娘家姓Weiser）是猶太人，出生於[[以色列|以色列]]，是運動教練<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2002/feb/24/foodanddrink.comedy|title=Mutha of invention|work=The Guardian|date=2002-02-24|accessdate=2018-04-24|archive-date=2018-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180421150932/https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2002/feb/24/foodanddrink.comedy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=bookref1>{{cite book|title=Sacha Baron Cohen: The Unauthorized Biography: From Cambridge to Kazakhstan|author=Tracy, K.|date=2007|publisher=St. Martin's Press|isbn=9781429993937|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=lqMEpeNCwL0C|page=10|accessdate=2014-11-22|archive-date=2014-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129122640/http://books.google.ca/books?id=lqMEpeNCwL0C|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的父親Gerald Baron Cohen是[[猶太人|猶太人]]，出生於[[倫敦|倫敦]]並住在[[威爾士|威爾士]]，經營著一間服飾店<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0056187/bio|title=Sacha Baron Cohen - Biography|work=IMDb|accessdate=2018-04-24|archive-date=2018-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180312222716/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0056187/bio|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=moment>{{cite journal|url=http://www.momentmag.com/moment/issues/2010/08/Baron-Cohen.html|title=The Provocative Baron Cohen Clan|work=[[Moment_(magazine)|Moment]]|date=July–August 2010|accessdate=2010-07-31|first=Sarah|last=Glazer|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100726213426/http://www.momentmag.com/moment/issues/2010/08/Baron-Cohen.html|archivedate=2010年7月26日}}</ref><ref name=bwhsosg>{{Cite book|last=Marquis Who's Who|title=Who's who in Finance and Industry, Volume 32|publisher=Marquis Who's Who.|year=2001|page=38}}</ref>。他的哥哥Erran Baron Cohen是作曲家<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/15104/|title=The musical Baron Cohen brother comes into his own|last=Pfefferman|first=Naomi|date=2007-07-13|work=Jewish Journal|accessdate=2018-05-25|archive-date=2018-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180525205042/http://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/15104/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的外祖母曾經是芭蕾舞者，現在居住在以色列<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/the-man-behind-the-mustache-20061130|title=Sacha Baron Cohen: The Man Behind the Mustache|author=|last=Strauss|first=Neil|date=2006-11-30|work=|newspaper=Rolling Stone|accessdate=2018-05-25|archive-date=2018-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180525204457/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/the-man-behind-the-mustache-20061130|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

拜伦·柯恩是犹太人<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.npr.org/templates/transcript/transcript.php?storyId=106695556|title=An Interview With The Real Sacha Baron Cohen|author=|date=2009-07-16|work=|newspaper=National Public Radio|accessdate=2018-05-25|quote=Sacha Baron Cohen: "I'd say that I'm very, very proud of my Jewish identity. I'm proud to be a Jew"|archive-date=2018-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180526040951/https://www.npr.org/templates/transcript/transcript.php?storyId=106695556|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jta.org/2016/02/25/life-religion/before-ali-g-sacha-baron-cohen-played-a-sweaty-hasidic-jew|title=Before Ali G, Sacha Baron Cohen played a sweaty Hasidic Jew|work=JTA - Jewish news|date=2016-02-25|accessdate=2018-04-24|archive-date=2018-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180425001250/https://www.jta.org/2016/02/25/life-religion/before-ali-g-sacha-baron-cohen-played-a-sweaty-hasidic-jew|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/news/sacha-baron-cohen-the-men-in-his-life-1675107.html|title=Sacha Baron Cohen: The men in his life|author=|date=2009-04-27|work=|newspaper=The Independent|accessdate=2018-05-25|language=|quote=He was born in 1971, the youngest of three boys in a middle-class Jewish family from west London.|archive-date=2018-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702131623/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/news/sacha-baron-cohen-the-men-in-his-life-1675107.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在一個正統派猶太教（Orthodox Jewish）家庭長大<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/go/london/film/profile-sacha-baron-cohen-and-the-making-of-bruno-6772832.html|title=Profile: Sacha Baron Cohen and the making of Bruno|work=London Evening Standard|date=2009-06-18|accessdate=2018-04-24|archive-date=2018-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180424202450/https://www.standard.co.uk/go/london/film/profile-sacha-baron-cohen-and-the-making-of-bruno-6772832.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Rob|last=Eshman|url=http://jewishjournal.com/mobile_20111212/103852/|title=Sacha Baron Cohen To Howard Stern: You inspired me [AUDIO]|work=Jewish Journal|date=2012-05-08|accessdate=2018-04-24|archive-date=2018-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180424202855/http://jewishjournal.com/mobile_20111212/103852/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而且能說一口流利的[[希伯來語|希伯來語]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.today.com/popculture/you-israelis-do-when-it-comes-borat-wbna16207852|title=You like? Israelis do when it comes to ‘Borat’|work=TODAY show|date=2006-12-15|accessdate=2018-04-24|archive-date=2018-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180424202713/https://www.today.com/popculture/you-israelis-do-when-it-comes-borat-wbna16207852|dead-url=no}}</ref>。是三兄弟中年齡最小的<ref name=telegraph>{{cite news|last = Mount|first = Harry|title = Kazakhstan launches propaganda campaign against Borat|work = The Daily Telegraph|date = 2006-09-15|url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1528944/Kazakhstan-launches-propaganda-campaign-against-Borat.html|accessdate = 2006-11-06|location = London|archive-date = 2008-06-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080611095017/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1528944/Kazakhstan-launches-propaganda-campaign-against-Borat.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

