==爭議==
===種族歧視===
拜伦·科恩和[[克里斯·洛克|克里斯·洛克]]在[[第88屆奧斯卡金像獎#亚洲人玩笑话争议|88屆奧斯卡頒獎典禮上開亞裔的玩笑]]，遭公眾批評，後來主辦方公開道歉<ref>{{cite news|last1=Deerwester |first1=Jayme |title=Academy apologizes for Asian joke at Oscars, announces new leadership roles |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/03/16/motion-picture-academy-apology-diversity-membership-leadership-changes/81860722/ |access-date=July 29, 2016 |work=USA Today |date=March 16, 2016 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723211403/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/03/16/motion-picture-academy-apology-diversity-membership-leadership-changes/81860722/ |archive-date=July 23, 2016}}</ref>。

